list.name: Default
list.comment: Important changes: - Downloader synchronization pieces are extracted to separate methods - Asynchronous ChannelWriter is added - Fixed issues in Downloader.initialize and Download.process - Download details are added to log output - Downloader.run test is added

task.summary: JBDownloader library: let the battle begin!
Making lbrary infrastructure: - junit dependency added - log4j dependency added - working on Download initialization
Following features are implemented: - Http HEAD parser - Download initialization - Download buffers querying
Here we are! Now it is possible to download one hardcoded url.
Executors pool is fixed in Downloader
Simplifying download & downloader: - async channel reader extracted to specific class - Download public interface is changed
Base functions binded to the GUI
Comments are added for all important types and methods

Important changes: - Downloader synchronization pieces are extracted to separate methods - Asynchronous ChannelWriter is added - Fixed issues in Downloader.initialize and Download.process - Download details are added to log output - Downloader.run test is added
